<p>Focus on buying-intent keywords first. Someone searching "best moving companies Tampa" has an upcoming move and is comparing options. That lead is worth 10x more than someone searching "how to pack dishes."</p>
<h3>Informational Keywords for Content Marketing</h3>
<p>These keywords attract people earlier in the moving process. They build trust and <a href="/glossary/organic-traffic/">organic traffic</a> over time.</p>
<ul>
<li>"how much do movers cost"</li>
<li>"moving checklist"</li>
