<h2>On-Page SEO for Moving Company Websites</h2>
<p>Your website is your 24/7 sales rep. On-page SEO ensures Google can read it, understand it, and rank it for the terms your customers search.</p>
<h3>Title Tags and Meta Descriptions</h3>
<p>Every page needs a unique title tag under 60 characters. Include your target keyword and city.</p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
<thead>
<tr>
